903
00:44:16,420 --> 00:44:18,060
Guards, take him!

904
00:44:18,060 --> 00:44:18,900
Have mercy.

905
00:44:19,020 --> 00:44:20,780
Your Majesty, please have mercy.

906
00:44:21,060 --> 00:44:22,940
- Father, please save Yuchi.
- Father.

907
00:44:22,940 --> 00:44:24,860
- Father.
- Father.

908
00:44:24,860 --> 00:44:26,260
- Yuchi.
- Yuchi.

909
00:44:26,260 --> 00:44:27,100
Mom!

910
00:44:27,380 --> 00:44:28,220
Mom!

911
00:44:28,940 --> 00:44:29,780
Father!

